fields.name: null security
fields.description: Beware, you are in an unsafe area. You could be attacked at any time, you're on your own.

fields.name: low security
fields.description: Be careful, security is poor in this area and the authorities will find it difficult to defend you.

fields.name: intermediate security
fields.description: It's not a highly secure area, but it's not a lawless one either, so just be careful.

fields.name: high security
fields.description: Here you are safe and secure, with security forces on call at all times and at very short notice.
